*Versions last checked: {{ last_check }}*

{% if summary is defined %}
## Summary

- :material-check-circle:{ .current } Current: {{ summary.current_count }}
- :material-close-circle:{ .outdated } Outdated: {{ summary.outdated_count }}
{% if summary.error_count %}- :material-alert-circle: Errors: {{ summary.error_count }}{% endif %}
